1. *Vaših* ideja nema granica. (Your ideas have no bounds.)
2. Mi smo spremni da prihvatimo *vaših* prijedloga. (We are ready to accept your suggestions.)
3. Svi smo ponosni na *vaših* uspeha. (We are all proud of your successes.)
4. Oni su postigli zapanjujuće rezultate uz pomoć *vaših* instrukcija. (They achieved remarkable results with your instructions.)
5. Probali smo da pratimo *vaših* saveta. (We tried to follow your advice.)